name: 无路可退
description:
Whether God or the headset pressed the forward button for us, do we have the means to resist?
Start a dramatic high-speed shooting journey with Chicken Cluck and help Chicken Cluck master his own destiny.


Kill enemies continuously to gain acceleration! Use enemy attacks to leap over cliffs!
Challenge yourself to pass the speed, can you go faster?


Multiple challenges, not just shooting and jumping! More mysteries for you to solve!
